  "details": "Vim is an advanced text editor that seeks to provide the power of the de-facto Unix editor 'Vi', with a more complete feature set. Vim is a highly configurable text editor built to enable efficient text editing. It is an improved version of the vi editor distributed with most UNIX systems.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nUse after free in utf_ptr2char in GitHub repository vim/vim prior to 8.2.4646.(CVE-2022-1154)\n\nUse after free in append_command in GitHub repository vim/vim prior to 8.2. This vulnerability is capable of crashing software, Bypass Protection Mechanism, Modify Memory, and possible remote execution(CVE-2022-1616)",
